We need rapid growth to meet the wishful expectations of our retirement plans and our runaway welfare states. We need science and technology to dig us out of our deep economic and financial hole, even though most of us cannot separate science from superstition or technology from magic. [[http://www.instapaper.com/text?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalreview.com%2Farticles%2F278758%2Fend-future-peter-thiel|The End of the Future - Peter Thiel]]
