Who can speak about the true health of the ever-expanding universe of human knowledge, given how complex, esoteric, and specialized the many scientific and technological fields have become? When any given field takes half a lifetime of study to master, who can compare and contrast and properly weight the rate of progress in nanotechnology and cryptography and superstring theory and 610 other disciplines? [[http://www.instapaper.com/text?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalreview.com%2Farticles%2F278758%2Fend-future-peter-thiel|The End of the Future - Peter Thiel]]
