Consider the most literal instance of non-acceleration: We are no longer moving faster. [[http://www.instapaper.com/text?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalreview.com%2Farticles%2F278758%2Fend-future-peter-thiel|The End of the Future - Peter Thiel]]
